# Serverless Task Manager on AWS

Built by Anthony Atuegwu  
Email: mrtony13@gmail.com

## AWS Services Used
- Amazon S3 (Frontend upload)
- AWS Amplify (Hosting)
- Amazon Cognito (Auth)
- Amazon API Gateway
- AWS Lambda
- Amazon DynamoDB

## What This Project Does
- Users log in securely
- Create, view, update, delete tasks
- Data stored in DynamoDB
- Fully serverless

